{"tid":1838081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好奇小寶寶入嚟] 點解源頭下下都係蝙蝠","createTime":"2020-01-24T01:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T03:50:23.000Z","uid":337449,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8f08f0bbe74043e2277ac9f950a54b9d795b39bf","tid":1838081,"uid":337449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"蝙蝠係一個強勁病毒宿主， 已發現嘅大概有68種可傳染人類嘅病毒<br />\n<br />\n先睇下同蝙蝠有關嘅人傳人大型致命疫症:<br />\n1997澳洲梅南高病毒<br />\n<strong>蝙蝠 -&gt; 豬-&gt; 人</strong><br />\n1997－1999 馬來西亞亨尼巴病毒<br />\n<strong>蝙蝠 -&gt; 豬-&gt; 人</strong><br />\n2003 SARS<br />\n<strong>蝙蝠 -&gt; 果子狸 -&gt; 人</strong><br />\n2012 中東呼吸綜合症<br />\n<strong>蝙蝠/駱駝 -&gt; 人</strong><br />\n2014 伊波拉病毒<br />\n<strong>蝙蝠 -&gt; 猩猩/馬騮/羚羊/豬 -&gt;人</strong><br />\n<br />\n到今次2020年武漢肺炎新型冠狀病毒，初步研究: <br />\n<strong>蝙蝠 -&gt; 蛇 -&gt;人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">點解蝙蝠咁多病菌病毒, 而且成日輸出比其他動物？</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題，基本上有兩個講法：<br />\n有啲科學家認為只係一場數字遊戲。<br />\n大多數嘅哺乳類動物都攜有可傳播比人類嘅病毒。只係因為蝙蝠數量多，物種亦多，所以傳播疾病率高亦不足為奇 。<br />\n <br />\n有啲對認為蝙蝠嘅獨特生理同埋習性，令佢哋成為一個流動病毒庫。 <br />\n大致原因有二：<br />\n<br />\n1. 大部分品種嘅蝙蝠係<ins>群居動物</ins>， 群體大小小至一百幾十隻，多至幾千隻。呢種棲息習慣大大增加咗病原體係蝙蝠之間傳播既機會 (就好似人類傷風感冒咁，係人多嘅地方惹到病嘅機會提高)。<br />\n<br />\n2. 蝙蝠全球<ins>分佈廣泛</ins>，對人類同畜養動物的影響相對亦大。 加上蝙蝠具飛行能力， 流動性高，因此能夠係更廣泛的地理區域傳播疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">咁點解佢哋自己又無事呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n學者認為<ins>蝙蝠同攜帶的病原體之間，存在著某種平衡</ins>。係人類和其他哺乳動物中, 只要對其中一種病原性病毒的免疫失效，就會引發嚴重既疾病。<br />\n <ins>但係蝙蝠體內有一種防禦系統</ins>： 喺進化嘅過程中，蝙蝠適應飛行呢個技能可能導致佢地有先天多重免疫和 DNA 損傷修復基因，所以蝙蝠可以同體內嘅病毒共存，而自身唔會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n(以上係小弟睇完新聞後大惑不解，然後隨手search完再整理下happy share。 大家隨便補充更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後，大家記得帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其是當身邊有食蝙蝠嘅人嘅時候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/4827511/bats-viruses-diseases-pandemihttps://www.wired.com/2014/10/bats-ebola-disease-reservoir-hosts/https://time.com/4827511/bats-viruses-diseases-pandemic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F4827511%2Fbats-viruses-diseases-pandemihttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2014%2F10%2Fbats-ebola-disease-reservoir-hosts%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F4827511%2Fbats-viruses-diseases-pandemic%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=18daadf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/4827511/bats-viruses-diseases-pandemihttps://www.wired.com/2014/10/bats-ebola-disease-reservoir-hosts/https://time.com/4827511/bats-viruses-diseases-pandemic/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2020/01/22/health/snakes-wuhan-coronavirus-outbreak-conversation-partner/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2Fhealth%2Fsnakes-wuhan-coronavirus-outbreak-conversation-partner%2Findex.html&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=0de44587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2Fhealth%2Fsnakes-wuhan-coronavirus-outbreak-conversation-partner%2Findex.html&h=c853a19f\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/01/22/health/snakes-wuhan-coronavirus-outbreak-conversation-partner/index.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/health/zgngnya.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhealth%2Fzgngnya.html&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=d416b2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/health/zgngnya.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2018/02/180222145005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedaily.com%2Freleases%2F2018%2F02%2F180222145005.htm&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=acc91c22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2018/02/180222145005.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2533b7ae4399b48d0996ac6d7d6eb4ab97e91876","tid":1838081,"uid":162008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\nA: 支持，連OT 都無，冒咁大風險,會死人！<br />\nB: 唔支持，置市民安危於不顧，不道德<br />\n<br />\n仲等咩, 快黎投票啦!<br />\n分享自香港地投票 HKVOTE<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FTopic.php%3Fid%3D1008&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=0746b830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1008</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手Wtsapp, FB 散出去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a2c72efbfa1afe27ece2d71dd810ffe8e0fc51a7","tid":1838081,"uid":29130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"怪唔之得BATMAN咁勁"},{"pid":"944862faabec5c070e655f8a771e0c8cc70e3528","tid":1838081,"uid":167536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:41:02.000Z","msg":"屌邊個會想放佢地入口"},{"pid":"66d531649cfa9165cf3defd8f7925a9f4b86c205","tid":1838081,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"你係咪鳩吹架<br />\n關乜野防禦系統事<br />\n純粹果D病毒係蝙蝠身上唔會發, 一直潛復之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9daf0fdf66d22670aece8b000d8334de45cb1f02","tid":1838